Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就把你玩个够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:01.80,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}S\Nh\Ni\Nn\Ne\N!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Lan Lan Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真高兴啊  简直爽的没边儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}有什么不愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:08.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}W\Nh\Ny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:13.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}马上就抛到脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:11.50,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}F\Ni\Nn\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:15.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:14.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Lan Lan Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.04,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}24小时在一起也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:22.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就像双生子亲子或者克隆细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:24.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就完全没有必要恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:27.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那个和这个完全完全没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}吵架的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:28.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}F\Ni\Ng\Nh\Nt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:32.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}心情很不好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:30.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}D\No\Nw\Nn\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:34.88,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}想要独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.38,0:01:33.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}S\Nh\No\Nc\Nk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:39.75,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}忽然发现你们就在身边  要死一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:42.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}为什么呢  只想在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.60,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你在一起  时间过得飞快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:47.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真高兴  实在太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.76,0:01:49.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不愧是最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎怎怎怎怎怎怎怎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么回事啊  这高到异常的同步率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}总是吵吵闹闹  给邻居带来不少烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}现在几点了  一会儿去吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:58.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}完全不明白怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:02:01.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那·又·怎·么·样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:02.28,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}比想象中好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么说呢  就是最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:04.76,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}再·怎·么·说  咱们都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:05.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好朋友  嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}极上  友情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}事事都要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}锵啦锵  锵啦锵…锵
