Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:20.29,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かなうならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:26.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼がほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:30.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この背中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.15,0:22:35.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:48.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}白い翼つけてください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:54.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この大空に翼をひろげ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.11,0:22:58.92,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}飛んで行きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:04.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみのない自由な空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:09.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼はためかせ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:12.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}行きたい
